Sentencas: Porous perovskites ceramics are very important components in solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Fabrication of La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ Porous Ceramics Using a Phase-Leaching Method

Sentencas: In the present work, porous ceramics of perovskite-type La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-delta with a controllable microstructure are successfully fabricated using a phase leaching method.
Titulo: Fabrication of La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ Porous Ceramics Using a Phase-Leaching Method

Sentencas: Sodium carbonate and La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-delta are processed to dual-phase ceramics, and then sodium carbonate is dissolved in water to leave connected pore channels.
Titulo: Fabrication of La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ Porous Ceramics Using a Phase-Leaching Method

Sentencas: The La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-delta porous ceramic obtained was characterized with an average pore size of 200 nm and a grain size of 250 nm by the SEM method.
Titulo: Fabrication of La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ Porous Ceramics Using a Phase-Leaching Method
